Package: metaFunc
Type: Package
Title: An R package for comprehensive visualization of functional annotations by combining taxonomy
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Xiaorui", "Dong", email = "xiaonui8@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Xiaorui Dong <xiaonui8@163.com>
Description: metaFunc is an R package for visualizing function annotation and involved 
    taxonomic classification. It introduce a complex combination chart composed of bar plot 
    and icicle plot to display the results. Furthermore, users can use icicle plot and sankey 
    diagram to layered view complex hierarchies of metagenomic classifications. metaFunc 
    supports both function call and a user-friendly graphical interface to meet different needs.
